## Entities in Clean Architecture

Integrating DDD with Clean Architecture:

```
Clean Architecture                    DDD Building Blocks
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Entities ──────────────────────────▶ Aggregates, Entities, VOs
Use Cases ────────────────────────▶ Application Services, Commands
Interface Adapters ────────────────▶ Repositories (interface), Controllers
Frameworks ───────────────────────▶ Repositories (impl), External Services
```

